    "The controller creates flow rules and policies for the flow tables to manage the workload in the infrastructure layer [41].",
    "It's worth noting that the control layer maintains QoS requirements in terms of network status monitoring and topology discovery, as well as making load-balancing choices based on the application layer's specifications [43,44].",
